# Outline Style

## Usage

Please refer to the documentation on the Tailwind CSS website

## Compatibility

| Class                  | Support     |
| ---------------------- | ----------- |
| ```
outline-none
```   | 🌐 Web only |
| ```
outline
```        | 🌐 Web only |
| ```
outline-dashed
``` | 🌐 Web only |
| ```
outline-dotted
``` | 🌐 Web only |
| ```
outline-double
``` | 🌐 Web only |
